{
  "texts": [
    "The learn gate serves as a memory to store short-term memory results coupled with input values.",
    "The forget gate serves as the long-term memory of the token sequence.",
    "The remember gate serves as a memory that stores short-term and long-term memory.",
    "This gate will later become a new long-term in the following sequence.",
    "The use gate is tasked with storing short-term and long-term memory, which subsequently becomes the new short-term memory for the next sequence."
  ]
}